from jaskew joseph askew subject re dir yassin in article hm harry mamaysky write from myth and fact by leonard j davi near east research inc great someone will be post from of the elder of zion next unlike the plo almost exclusive focu on civilian target at thi time the plo do not exist and would not for the next year you know that do you perhap you might want to add up all the jewish civilian kill during the war i opt for the massacre at deir yassin which do you think be the greater in however eric silver of the guardian britain interview a survivor mophammed sammmy who testify that out of a population of be kill while we be talk about thi man i have include more of hi testimony that harry naturally do not use nor do myth and fact i wonder why no doubt he wa lie right harry the reason wa mainly economic that be to capture booty in order to maintain the basis which we have then establish with very poor resource the main idea despite thi remain the conquest of the village by force of arm something which wa then unknown in the country and become a turn point in jewish military operation yehuda lapidot jabontinsky archive testimony apart from the military discussion the lehi put forward a proposal to liqui date the resident of the village after the conquest in order to show the arab what happen when the izl and the lehi set out together on an operation and for another main reason it would cause a great uproar throughout the land and would be an important turn point in the course of the battle the clear aim wa to break the arab morale and raise somewhat the morale of the jewish commu nity in jerusalem which have be hit hard time after time especially recenctly by the desecration of jewish body which fell into arab hand yehuda lapidot jabotinsky archive testimony a quote by yisrael segal in the deir yassin file publish by koteret rashit january so it wa like the holocaust more like lidice a warn a punishment collective and inflict on unarm innocent just not a through wh