how and fact do not see fit to include thi too after all if he be reliable enough to report casualty why not the actual event what do you say about thi harry in the exchange that follow fmy man be kill and a dozen be wound by noon time the battle wa over and the shoot have cease although there wa a calm the village have not yet surrender the irgun and lehi man come out of hide and begin to the house they shoot whoever they saw woman and child include the commander do not try and stop the massacre i plead with the commander to order hi man to cease fire but to no avail in the meantime twenty five arab have be load on a truck and drive through mahane-yehuda and zichron yosef at the end of the drive they be take to the quarry bvetween deir yassin and givat shaul and murder in cold blood meir interview with yediot ahronot joseph askew gauche and proud in the autumn stillnes see the pleiade jaskew remote in thorny desert fell the grief disclaimer sue see if i care north of my tent the sky must end somwhere actually i rather like brenda beyond the pale the river murmur on 